---
title: Carb Smart Pepper Pesto Turkey Stew with Carrots and Green Peppers
description: A low starch twist on goulash — this stew has hearty turkey, loads of veggies, a bit of hearty potato and a swirl of roasted pepper pesto! This bright dollop takes the place of powdered paprika!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragout-de-dinde-au-pesto-de-poivrons-c3c43749.jpg
